---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Contact - Bidwell Capital" description="Get in touch with Bidwell Capital.">
  <section class="hero-sm">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section-label fade-up fade-up-1">Contact</span>
      <h1 class="fade-up fade-up-2">Start a conversation</h1>
      <p class="fade-up fade-up-3">We want to build relationships for life, and that starts with a conversation. No pitch, no pressure. Just two people talking about goals.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="contact-grid">
        <div>
          <div class="card contact-card">
            <span class="section-label">Email</span>
            <a href="mailto:team@bidwellcapitalfund.com" class="contact-link">team@bidwellcapitalfund.com</a>
            <p style="margin-top: 0.75rem;">Best way to reach us. We typically respond within 24 hours.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="card contact-card" style="margin-top: 1.5rem;">
            <span class="section-label">Location</span>
            <p style="color: var(--text-primary); font-size: 1.125rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Northern California</p>
            <p>Chico, CA area. Available for virtual meetings nationwide.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="card contact-card" style="margin-top: 1.5rem;">
            <span class="section-label">Podcast</span>
            <a href="https://www.wealthindependencepod.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color: var(--text-primary); font-size: 1.125rem; display: block; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; text-decoration: none;">Wealth Independence Podcast <span style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--accent);">&rarr;</span></a>
            <p>Conversations about building wealth through real assets, tax strategy, and financial independence.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div>
          <div class="card" style="padding: 2rem;">
            <h3 style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">What to expect</h3>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">When you reach out, here is what the process looks like:</p>
            <div class="process-steps">
              <div class="step">
                <span class="step-num">01</span>
                <div>
                  <strong style="color: var(--text-primary); display: block; margin-bottom: 0.25rem;">Initial conversation</strong>
                  <p>We will discuss your goals, your situation, and whether there is a mutual fit. This is about building a relationship, not a sales call.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="step">
                <span class="step-num">02</span>
                <div>
                  <strong style="color: var(--text-primary); display: block; margin-bottom: 0.25rem;">Review materials</strong>
                  <p>If there is a mutual fit, we will share our current offering documents and fund details.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="step">
                <span class="step-num">03</span>
                <div>
                  <strong style="color: var(--text-primary); display: block; margin-bottom: 0.25rem;">Invest</strong>
                  <p>Complete subscription documents and fund your investment. We handle the rest.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="step">
                <span class="step-num">04</span>
                <div>
                  <strong style="color: var(--text-primary); display: block; margin-bottom: 0.25rem;">Stay informed</strong>
                  <p>We are always available to answer questions. Most of our deals provide monthly updates so you know exactly how your capital is working. Want to see our communication style before investing? Ask about our Deal Observer program. You can follow along on active deals even if you haven't invested yet.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Calendly. Direct iframe (no widget.js wrapper), only one theme rendered, eager-loaded. -->
  <section id="book" class="section" style="background: var(--bg-secondary);">
    <div class="container" style="text-align: center;">
      <span class="section-label">Schedule a Call</span>
      <h2>Book a consultation</h2>
      <p style="margin-bottom: 2rem; max-width: 55ch; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;">Pick a time that works for you. No commitment, no pressure. Just a conversation about your goals.</p>
      <div class="calendly-wrap">
        <div id="calendly-skeleton" class="calendly-skeleton" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        <iframe
          id="calendly-frame"
          title="Schedule a consultation with Bidwell Capital"
          src="https://calendly.com/adampenn/bc-consultation?background_color=f5f0eb&text_color=1a1816&primary_color=c48a5a&hide_gdpr_banner=1"
          data-theme-loaded="light"
          width="100%"
          height="700"
          frameborder="0"
          loading="eager"
          style="display:block; border:0; min-width:320px; background:transparent;"
        ></iframe>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<script is:inline>
  // Render only the theme-matching Calendly iframe. No widget.js wrapper, no second iframe.
  (function() {
    var BASE = 'https://calendly.com/adampenn/bc-consultation';
    var PARAMS = {
      dark:  '?background_color=1a1816&text_color=e8e0d6&primary_color=c48a5a&hide_gdpr_banner=1',
      light: '?background_color=f5f0eb&text_color=1a1816&primary_color=c48a5a&hide_gdpr_banner=1'
    };
    var frame = document.getElementById('calendly-frame');
    var skeleton = document.getElementById('calendly-skeleton');
    if (!frame) return;
    function apply() {
      var theme = document.documentElement.getAttribute('data-theme');
      var key = theme === 'light' ? 'light' : 'dark';
      var url = BASE + PARAMS[key];
      if (frame.getAttribute('data-theme-loaded') !== key) {
        frame.src = url;
        frame.setAttribute('data-theme-loaded', key);
      }
    }
    frame.addEventListener('load', function() {
      if (frame.src.indexOf('about:blank') !== -1) return;
      if (skeleton) {
        skeleton.style.opacity = '0';
        setTimeout(function() { if (skeleton) skeleton.style.display = 'none'; }, 250);
      }
    });
    apply();
    new MutationObserver(function(ms) {
      for (var i = 0; i < ms.length; i++) if (ms[i].attributeName === 'data-theme') { apply(); break; }
    }).observe(document.documentElement, { attributes: true });
  })();

  // If the user lands with #book in the URL, smooth-scroll to the Calendly section after layout.
  (function() {
    if (window.location.hash !== '#book') return;
    function scrollToBook() {
      var el = document.getElementById('book');
      if (!el) return;
      el.scrollIntoView({ behavior: 'smooth', block: 'start' });
    }
    if (document.readyState === 'loading') {
      document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() { setTimeout(scrollToBook, 50); });
    } else {
      setTimeout(scrollToBook, 50);
    }
  })();
</script>

<style>
  .hero-sm {
    padding: 5rem 0 2rem;
  }
  .hero-sm h1 { margin: 0.5rem 0 1rem; }
  .hero-sm p { font-size: 1.125rem; max-width: 60ch; }

  .contact-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .contact-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 3rem;
    }
  }

  .contact-card {
    padding: 1.5rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 400px) {
    .contact-card {
      padding: 1.25rem;
    }
  }

  .contact-link {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 4vw, 1.5rem);
    color: var(--accent);
    display: block;
    margin-top: 0.25rem;
    word-break: break-all;
  }

  .contact-link:hover {
    color: var(--accent-hover);
  }

  .process-steps {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.25rem;
  }

  .step {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .step-num {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--accent);
    line-height: 1;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 2rem;
  }

  .step p {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
  }

  .calendly-wrap {
    position: relative;
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    border-radius: 12px;
    overflow: hidden;
    min-height: 700px;
    background: var(--bg);
  }

  /* Shimmer skeleton while the Calendly iframe contents paint */
  .calendly-skeleton {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    border-radius: 12px;
    background:
      linear-gradient(
        90deg,
        var(--bg) 0%,
        var(--bg-elevated) 45%,
        var(--bg) 100%
      );
    background-size: 200% 100%;
    animation: calendly-shimmer 1.4s ease-in-out infinite;
    transition: opacity 0.25s ease;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 1;
  }
  @keyframes calendly-shimmer {
    0%   { background-position: 200% 0; }
    100% { background-position: -200% 0; }
  }
  #calendly-frame {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
  }
</style>
